snippet.title: Terrordactyl Carnivore Gameplay
snippet.description:
*Occasionally making gaming videos

Terrordactyl Carnivore Gameplay

It's one of my favorite childhood games. This isn't the first time I played it and it sure isn't the highest score that I ever got. However I chose to upload this one because I felt like I played better than the other times. This game is perfect for killing time.
Song used in video: "My Songs Know What You Did In The Dark (Light 'Em Up)" by Fall Out Boy
